    This class contains methods and fields for handling the log process

    Common base class for all test classes designed to be executed within the JADE test suite framework

    Base class for agents performing tests within the JADE test suite framework.
    TestGroup
    Class representing a group of tests (often related to a given functionality) that have to be executed in sequence and require similar configuration, initialization and clean-up operations.
    TestGroupExecutor
    Generic behaviour that executes the tests included in a TestGroup object
    TestUtility
    Class including utility static methods for launching/killing agents, requesting generic AMS actions and creating remote JADE instances.
